'''布魯塞爾電車'''（{{lang-fr|Tramway de Bruxelles}}，{{lang-nl|Brusselse tram}}）是[[比利時|比利時]]首都及最大城市[[布魯塞爾|布魯塞爾]]的[[有軌電車|有軌電車]]系統，亦是全球十大的有軌電車系統，共20條路線<ref name="scheds">{{cite web |url=http://www.stib.be/horaires-dienstregeling.html?l=en |title=STIB - Timetables and real time |publisher=STIB/MIVB |year=2013 |accessdate=2013-09-15 |archive-date=2014-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106084257/http://www.stib.be/horaires-dienstregeling.html?l=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，總長度{{convert|138.9|km|mi}}<ref name="stats1">{{cite web |url=http://www.mivb.be/irj/go/km/docs/STIB-MIVB/INTERNET/attachments/Bilan_2011/STIB_FiguresStatistics_2011.pdf |title=Activity Report 2011 - Figures & statistics '11 |publisher=STIB/MIVB |page=08 |date= |accessdate=2013-09-15 |archive-date=2017-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223131019/http://www.mivb.be/irj/go/km/docs/STIB-MIVB/INTERNET/attachments/Bilan_2011/STIB_FiguresStatistics_2011.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，載客量每年超過一百萬<ref name="key figures">{{cite web|url=http://www.stib.be/figures.html?l=en |title=STIB - Key Figures |publisher=STIB |year=2013 |accessdate=2013-09-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928110355/http://www.stib.be/figures.html?l=en |archivedate=2013-09-28 }}</ref>。

